And, Pumbaa, you and me...

11
01:01:49.920 --> 01:01:51.680 
我们必须引那些土狼 远离 辛巴。
we've got to get those hyenas away from Simba.

12
01:01:51.760 --> 01:01:53.690 
呜,呜! 引他们进陷阱
Ooh, ooh! And lure them into the trap?

13
01:01:53.790 --> 01:01:56.730 
什么都瞒不过你。
Ho ho! Nothing gets past you.

14
01:01:56.760 --> 01:01:58.960 
来吧 ,Pumbaa,我们走。
Come on, Pumbaa, let's ride.

15
